text: Jhando Mari is a town and Union Council of Tando Allah Yaar District in the Sindh Province of Pakistan. It is part of Jhando Mari Taluka and is in the north of the district at 25°38'60N 68°54'0E,. The Union Council has 30,384 people. ==References== Category:Union councils of Tando Allahyar District
title: Jhando Mari
